a.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khans-dunki-shows-major-jump-in-us-market-after-trailer-release%2Farticleshow%2F105834070.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105834070.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20%26quot%3BDunki%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Rajkumar%20Hirani%2C%20sees%20a%20significant%20surge%20in%20US%20ticket%20sales%20after%20the%20trailer%20release%2C%20with%20a%20jump%20from%2030%20to%202001%20tickets%20in%20three%20days.%20Despite%20competition%20with%20%26quot%3BSalaar%2C%26quot%3B%20both%20films%20anticipate%20strong%20performances%20in%20India%20and%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Sign%20From%20BJP%20of%20Who%20Will%20Be%20Chief%20Ministers%3A%20Indecision%20or%20Strategy%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F23091003%2FBJP-states.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Five%20days%20after%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20won%20big%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20there%20was%20still%20no%20indication%20of%20who%20will%20be%20the%20chief%20ministers%20of%20these%20states.%20The%20party%20contested%20the%20elections%20with%20a%20model%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccollective%20leadership%E2%80%9D%20anchored%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20may%20be%20spoilt%20for%20choice%2C%20given%20the%20large%20mandate%20it%20received%2C%20one%20wonders%20if%20the%20%E2%80%98delay%E2%80%99%20was%20caused%20by%20indecision%2C%20failure%20in%20building%20consensus%20or%20if%20it%20is%20strategic.%20Either%20way%2C%20it%20is%20a%20commentary%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20transparency%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20appointed%20observers%20in%20the%20three%20states%2C%20following%20which%20legislature%20party%20meetings%20will%20be%20held.%20For%20Rajasthan%2C%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20Vinod%20Tawade%20and%20Saroj%20Pandey%20will%20be%20the%20observers%3B%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20observers%20are%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20K.%20Laxman%2C%20Asha%20Lakra%3B%20Union%20ministers%20Arjun%20Munda%20and%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal%2C%20and%20Dushyant%20Gautam%20will%20be%20the%20observers%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20centralised%20mode%20of%20functioning%20under%20Modi%20and%20his%20trusted%20lieutenant%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%20factionalism%20within%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20units%20of%20the%20party%20is%20no%20secret.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20recalled%20that%20after%20losing%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%20election%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20BJP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fbengaluru-news%2Fbjp-appoints-vokkaliga-strongman-r-ashok-as-leader-of-opposition-in-karnataka-101700232586770.html%5C%22%3Etook%20almost%20six%20months%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20deciding%20its%20leader%20of%20opposition.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20delay%20in%20picking%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20carrying%20out%20an%20organisational%20rejig%20was%20due%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfeud%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20camps%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20powerful%20national%20general%20secretary%20(organisation)%20B.L%20Santhosh%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20B.S.%20Yediyurappa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202017%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20a%20comprehensive%20victory%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20without%20declaring%20an%20official%20CM%20face%20%E2%80%93%20a%20strategy%20similar%20to%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Modi-led%20elections.%20The%20party%20took%20more%20than%20a%20week%20before%20zeroing%20in%20on%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%20Remarkably%2C%20Adityanath%20was%20not%20among%20the%20325%20elected%20NDA%20MLAs%20but%20a%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Gorakhpur%20and%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20he%20was%20planted%20to%20the%20top%20post%20by%20the%20central%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20in%20December%202023%2C%20with%20multiple%20claimants%20to%20the%20top%20post%20in%20the%20three%20states%2C%20speculation%20is%20rife%20whether%20the%20brass%2C%20which%20enjoys%20supreme%20authority%20in%20such%20matters%2C%20was%20unable%20to%20finalise%20its%20best%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20turned%20into%20a%20matter%20of%20political%20scrutiny%20on%20Thursday%2C%20when%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20wondered%20why%20the%20BJP%20was%20still%20unable%20to%20announce%20its%20CMs%20for%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%20of%20the%20Congress%20formally%20took%20charge%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20Telangana%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLess%20than%2024%20hours%20after%20the%20election%20results%20were%20out%20on%20December%203rd%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20was%20being%20criticised%20in%20the%20media%20by%20all%20and%20sundry%20for%20a%20so-called%20%E2%80%98delay%E2%80%99%20in%20appointing%20a%20CM%20for%20Telangana.%20Well%2C%20our%20CM%20was%20announced%20day%20before%20and%20is%20taking%20over%20at%201pm%20today%E2%80%A6Why%20is%20the%20BJP%20not%20being%20called%20out%20for%20what%20is%20actually%20a%20delay%3F%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20MP%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20also%20questioned%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20delay%20in%20deciding%20CMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20got%20a%20majority.%20The%20elected%20MLAs%20need%20to%20decide%20who%20will%20be%20the%20leader%20(CM).%20But%20that%20process%20has%20been%20done%20with%20in%20the%20BJP.%20Only%20two%20people%20decide%20who%20will%20be%20the%20CM.%20They%20are%20Narendra%20Modiji%20and%20Amit%20Shahji%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaturvedi%20told%20a%20news%20agency%20outside%20Parliament.%3Cbr%3E%5CnChaturvedi%20also%20linked%20it%20to%20the%20alleged%20vacuum%20in%20governance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20law-and-order%20situation%20in%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%93%20where%20the%20chief%20of%20a%20caste-based%20supremacist%20group%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fprominent-rajput-leader-gogamedi-shot-dead-protests-erupt-in-rajasthan%5C%22%3Emurdered%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20days%20after%20the%20results%20of%20the%20election%20%E2%80%93%20had%20collapsed.%20Had%20the%20Congress%20been%20in%20power%2C%20there%20would%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9C100%20TV%20debates%E2%80%9D%20on%20it%20already%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELarge%20sections%20of%20the%20media%20have%20played%20the%20story%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98delay%E2%80%99%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20anticipation%20and%20suspense%2C%20rather%20than%20asking%20questions%20of%20the%20decision-making%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20questions%20by%20the%20opposition%20parties%2C%20a%20national%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20told%20media%20persons%20in%20Bhopal%20that%20the%20wait%20could%20end%20on%20Sunday%2C%20December%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIs%20there%20something%20in%20the%20constitution%20which%20says%20that%20a%20CM%20must%20be%20announced%20in%20these%20many%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20party%20will%20declare%20the%20CMs%20when%20it%20finds%20it%20fit.%20When%20journalists%20asked%20Vijayvargiya%20if%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20choice%20for%20CM%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20would%20be%20someone%20from%20within%20its%20elected%20MLAs%20in%20the%20230-member%20assembly%20or%20someone%20else%2C%20he%20gave%20no%20clear%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08123205%2F404632135_901017344715452_4627480104197525111_n.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08123205%2F404632135_901017344715452_4627480104197525111_n.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08123205%2F404632135_901017344715452_4627480104197525111_n-300x163.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688252%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22543%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKailash%20Vijayvargiya.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2F%2FKailashOnline%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20delay%20mounting%2C%20there%20have%20been%20signs%20of%20muscle-flexing%20from%20some%20of%20the%20top%20contenders%20in%20these%20states.%20On%20Monday%2C%20Vasundhara%20Raja%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20minister%20who%20is%20hoping%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%2C%20met%20with%20around%2025%20MLAs%20at%20her%20residence%2C%20in%20what%20many%20perceived%20to%20be%20a%20show%20of%20strength.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20Raje%20met%20BJP%20president%20J.P.%20Nadda%20in%20Delhi.%20What%20transpired%20in%20the%20meeting%20was%20not%20publicly%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EC.P.%20Joshi%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Rajasthan%20president%2C%20downplayed%20Raje%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Delhi.%20Joshi%20told%20a%20news%20channel%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnatural%E2%80%9D%20for%20Raje%2C%20a%20party%20vice-president%2C%20to%20travel%20to%20Delhi%20and%20congratulate%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20the%20party%20on%20the%20recent%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Parliamentary%20Board%20of%20the%20party%20will%20decide%20%5Bwho%20will%20be%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20legislature%20party%5D.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20party%20worker%2C%20and%20whatever%20the%20top%20leadership%20will%20decide%20will%20be%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Joshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mps-lukewarm-response-assembly-polls%5C%22%3EEleven%20sitting%20BJP%20MPs%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20contested%20the%20elections%20were%20also%20elected%20to%20the%20assemblies%20and%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20possibility%20that%20they%20could%20get%20bigger%20roles%20in%20state%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20three%20current%20or%20former%20CMs%20in%20contention%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20MP%20%E2%80%93%20Raman%20Singh%2C%20Raje%20and%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%20may%20be%20facing%20a%20dilemma%3A%20stick%20with%20the%20old%20warhorses%2C%20also%20the%20most%20popular%20state%20leaders%2C%20or%20experiment%20with%20fresh%20faces%20to%20develop%20future%20leadership%20and%20strengthen%20the%20grip%20of%20the%20central%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20central%20leadership%20had%20cut%20Raje%20and%20Chouhan%20down%20to%20size%20was%20already%20indicated%20when%20they%20were%20not%20declared%20official%20CM%20candidates%20and%20the%20party%20decided%20to%20field%20several%20MPs%20in%20the%20state%20elections.%20That%20strategy%20may%20have%20worked%20electorally%20but%20how%20smoothly%20would%20it%20translate%20into%20power%20sharing%2C%20only%20time%20will%20tell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Raje%2C%20who%20has%20been%20active%20ever%20since%20the%20results%20were%20declared%2C%20Chouhan%20too%20has%20already%20made%20attempts%20to%20race%20ahead%20of%20others%20in%20the%20image%20game.%20On%20December%206%20and%207%2C%20he%20held%20workers%E2%80%99%20meets%20and%20Ladli%20Behna%20events%20in%20Chhindwara%20and%20Sheopur%2C%20respectively.%20He%20especially%20interacted%20with%20women%2C%20whom%20he%20has%20tried%20to%20cultivate%20as%20a%20voter%20base%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Chhindwara%2C%20which%20is%20Congress%20state%20president%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20turf%2C%20Chouhan%20launched%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Mission%2029%E2%80%99%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%20Chhindwara%20was%20the%20only%20parliamentary%20seat%20of%20the%2029%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20that%20the%20BJP%20failed%20to%20win%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChouhan%2C%20the%20Budhni%20MLA%20who%20hopes%20to%20become%20chief%20minister%20for%20the%20fifth%20time%2C%20credited%20the%20victory%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20faith%20in%20Modi%20but%20also%20asserted%20the%20role%20of%20the%20flagship%20schemes%20he%20ran%20for%20women%20as%20another%20reason%20for%20the%20big%20mandate.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20amazing%20journey%20from%20Ladli%20Laxmi%20to%20Ladli%20Behna%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chouhan%2C%20also%20crediting%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdouble-engine%20government%E2%80%9D%20for%20properly%20implementing%20the%20schemes%20of%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20a%20curious%20comment%20on%20the%20factors%20behind%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20win%20in%20MP%2C%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20seen%20as%20a%20rival%20of%20Chouhan%20for%20the%20CM%20post%2C%20tried%20to%20downplay%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Ladli%20Behna%20Scheme.%20This%20may%20be%20interpreted%20as%20his%20way%20of%20moderating%20the%20credit%20received%20by%20Chouhan%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20dominating%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWas%20there%20the%20Ladli%20Behna%20Yojana%20in%20Chhattisgarh%3F%20Was%20it%20there%20in%20Rajasthan%3F%20The%20victory%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20was%20a%20big%20win%20and%20bigger%20than%20MP%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vijayvargiya%20said%2C%20crediting%20%E2%80%9Conly%20and%20only%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%2C%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20and%20J.P.%20Nadda%20%E2%80%99s%20polling%20booth%20and%20panna%20pramukh%20yojanas%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20three%20wins.%20The%20common%20factor%20in%20these%20three%20states%20was%20the%20leadership%20of%20Modi%2C%20he%20insisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijayvargiya%2C%20the%20Indore-1%20MLA%2C%20was%20among%20the%20163%20BJP%20legislators%20elected%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702020575000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F23091003%2FBJP-states.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-delay-chief-ministers-indecision-strategy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20the%20centralised%20mode%20of%20functioning%20under%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%20factionalism%20within%20the%20party's%20state%20units%20of%20the%20party%20is%20no%20secret.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-delay-chief-ministers-indecision-strategy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Turns%20out%20Google's%20Gemini%20demo%20wasn't%20nearly%20as%20amazing%20as%20it%20seemed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20illustration%20of%20Google%20Gemini%20AI%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6572aa287a3c8094d5dae203%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22686%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGemini%20is%20Google's%20answer%20to%20ChatGPT.%3Cp%3ESOPA%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle's%20much-lauded%20demo%20of%20Gemini%20showed%20the%20AI%20responding%20in%20real-time%20to%20events%20on%20screen.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20the%20company%20confirmed%20it%20edited%20out%20the%20human%20intervention%20that%20made%20Gemini%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20made%20it%20to%20inspire%20developers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Google%20DeepMind's%20head%20of%20research.%3C%