20be%20tabled%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fr28o2ABVbB%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fr28o2ABVbB%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1732991828281237793%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%208%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20though%2C%20is%20well-prepped.%20The%20party%20issued%20a%20three-line%20whip%20(the%20strictest%20possible)%20to%20its%20MPs%20last%20evening%3B%20a%20three-line%20whip%20means%20MPs%20must%20be%20present%20and%20vote%20in%20line%20with%20the%20party's%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20was%20to%20have%20been%20tabled%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20this%20session%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20demanded%20a%20detailed%20discussion%20on%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20MP%20Danish%20Ali%2C%20one%20of%20the%20members%20of%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20told%20reporters%20Thursday%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20report%20is%20tabled%2C%20we%20will%20insist%20on%20a%20full-fledged%20discussion...%20the%20draft%20was%20adopted%20in%20two-and-a-half%20minutes%26quot%3B%2C%20referring%20to%20opposition%20claims%20the%20BJP-led%20committee%20rushed%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahua-moitra-lok-sabha-ethics-committee-danish-ali-over-in-minutes-danish-ali-on-mahua-moitra-report-committee-head-says-4561435%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BOver%20In%20Minutes%26quot%3B%3A%20Danish%20Ali%20On%20Mahua%20Moitra%20Report%2C%20Committee%20Head%20Says...%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahua%20Moitra%2C%2049%2C%20is%20accused%20of%20taking%20bribes%2C%20including%20Rs%202%20crore%20in%20cash%2C%20to%20ask%20questions%20critical%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20She%20has%20flatly%20denied%20t