ing%20%26quot%3Bwindfall%20gains%26quot%3B%20of%20Rs%20338%20crore%20to%20wholesale%20liquor%20dealers%20is%20%26quot%3Btentatively%26quot%3B%20backed%20by%20evidence.%20Mr%20Sisodia%20last%20week%20moved%20the%20court%20seeking%20a%20review%20of%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sisodia%20was%20first%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20on%20February%2026.%20He%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20two%20weeks%20later%2C%20on%20March%209%2C%20after%20a%20prolonged%20interrogation%20inside%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20Jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20implemented%20the%20revised%20liquor%20excise%20policy%20on%20November%2017%2C%202021%2C%20but%20it%20was%20scrapped%20less%20than%20a%20year%20later%20amid%20widespread%20allegations%20of%20corruption.%20Investigating%20agencies%20have%20claimed%20wholesalers'%20profit%20margins%20were%20arbitrarily%20increased%20from%20five%20to%2012%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fexplained-whats-the-delhi-liquor-policy-case-linked-to-arvind-kejriwals-aap-4537295%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENDTV%20Explains%20Delhi%20Liquor%20Policy%20Case%20Linked%20To%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20new%20policy%20resulted%20in%20cartelisation%20and%20those%20ineligible%20for%20liquor%20licences%20were%20favoured%20for%20monetary%20benefits.%20However%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20Manish%20Sisodia%20have%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing%20and%20said%20the%20new%20policy%20would%20have%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2