ty%20and%20could%20not%20situate%20Gandhi%20as%20a%20national%20leader%20of%20consequence%2C%20let%20alone%20an%20alternative%20to%20hugely%20popular%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20irrespective%20of%20a%20large%20number%20of%20analysts%20continuously%20listing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-assembly-elections-hat-trick-2024%5C%22%3Enegative%20impact%20of%20his%20majoritarian%20politics%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20society%2C%20the%20constitution%2C%20institutions%2C%20even%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20lone%20Telangana%20win%20shows%20that%20there%20is%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%20for%20the%20party.%20Add%20to%20this%20the%20earlier%20Karnataka%20victory%2C%20where%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20had%20used%20its%20entire%20institutional%20weight%2C%20but%20the%20Congress%20managed%20with%20leadership%20(both%20national%20and%20state)%2C%20cadre%2C%20a%20programme%20(populist%20or%20otherwise)%20and%20an%20agenda.%20The%20Yatra%20also%20contributed%2C%20in%20a%20small%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20297px)%2085vw%2C%20297px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22297%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22245%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20question%20of%20a%20non-Nehru-Gandhi%20presidentship%20has%20been%20addressed%20by%20electing%20octogenarian%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20the%20two%20weak%20points%20of%20this%20quest%20and%20process%20need%20underlining%20%E2%80%93%20first%2C%20the%20search%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98loyalist%E2%80%99%20(to%20the%20Gandhis)%20and%20second%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20neutralising%20the%20so-called%20party%20high%20command%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20his%20name.%20To%20his%20great%20credit%2C%20Kharge%20has%20been%20able%20to%20manage%20the%20party%2C%20iron%20out%20the%20leadership%20and%20organisational%20wrinkles%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20but%20he%20has%20fallen%20short%20of%20a%20fresh%20and%20dynamic%20plan%20for%20party-building.%20Second%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98loyalist%E2%80%99%20tag%20imposes%20limitation%20of%20his%20functioning%20within%20a%20circle%20drawn%20by%20the%20Gandhis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20remains%20the%20unannounced%20leader%20of%20the%20party%2C%20and%20Sonia%20and%20Priyanka%20have%20to%20be%20put%20up%20on%20similar%20pedestals%20when%20he%20and%20his%20team%20(if%20there%20is%20one)%20takes%20any%20organisational%20decision.%20This%20de-institutionalisation%20does%20not%20enthuse%20the%20cadre.%20Despite%20the%20party%20being%20in%20power%20in%20four%20states%2C%20and%20with%20shares%20in%20a%20couple%20more%2C%20it%20lacked%20a%20cadre%20that%20Kharge%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20building.%20Nor%20is%20he%20initiating%20a%20dynamic%20political%20recruitment%20process.%20He%20could%20resolve%20leadership%20contradictions%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20but%20cracks%20in%20the%20latter%20two%20have%20impacted%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20fortunes.%20In%20each%2C%20the%20cadre%20is%20divided%20behind%20the%20warring%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20and%20his%20team%20also%20can%E2%80%99t%20articulate%20alternative%20national%20and%20state-wise%20narratives%20for%20lifting%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20image.%20Neither%20during%20the%20Yatra%2C%20nor%20during%20his%20campaign%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20the%20three%20poll-bound%20states%20could%20Rahul%20spell%20out%20a%20narrative%20that%20situated%20him%20and%20the%20party%20as%20the%20political%20alternative%20to%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP.%20Ever%20since%20the%20Congress%20lost%20its%20pre-eminence%20in%201989%20and%20the%20Mandal%20and%20Mandir%20movements%20built%20up%20during%20the%201990s%2C%20the%20party%20has%20failed%20to%20challenge%20them.%20Rahul%20lost%20a%20golden%20opportunity%2C%20when%20his%20party%20led%20the%20UPA%20coalition%20for%20a%20decade%2C%20in%20building%20a%20national%20as%20well%20as%20several%20local%20narratives%20that%20could%20situate%20the%20party%20as%20a%20dominant%20choice%20against%20sectarian%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20wonder%2C%20when%20Narendra%20Modi%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20RSS%20and%20select%20corporates%20he%20had%20gathered%20during%20his%20chief%20ministership%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20at%20a%20complete%20loss%20about%20how%20to%20articulate%20itself.%20It%20could%20not%20produce%20any%20script%20to%20beat%20majoritarian%2C%20resurgent%20Hindutva%2C%20which%20termed%20inclusivity%20as%20minority%20appeasement.%20This%20narrative%20resonated%20with%20large%20sections%20in%20the%20Hindi%20belt%20as%20never%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20three%20states%20lost%2C%20the%20Congress%20narrative%20was%20to%20ape%20the%20BJP.%20The%20soft%20Hindutva%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20declared%20himself%20to%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98Hanuman%20%3Cem%3Ebhakta%20%3C%2Fem%3E(worshipper)%E2%80%99%2C%20put%20up%20a%20Hanuman%20idol%2C%20even%20courted%20controversial%20Bageshwar%20Dham%20guru%20Dhirendra%20Krishna%20Shastri%2C%20could%20not%20be%20a%20match%20to%20the%20deeply%20entrenched%20Hindutva%20narrative.%20Rahul%20did%20not%20only%20allow%20this%2C%20he%20too%20would%20visit%20temples%20and%20appear%20in%20public%20with%20his%20vermillion%20on%20his%20forehead%2C%20like%20Modi.%20Under%20his%20leadership%2C%20an%20apprehensive%20Congress%20never%20raised%20its%20voice%20for%20minority%20communities%2C%20for%20fear%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20accuse%20it%20of%20minority%20appeasement.%20Naturally%2C%20their%20programmes%20also%20do%20not%20have%20anything%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20needed%20to%20be%20imaginative%20about%20the%20charge%20of%20revdi%20culture%2C%20which%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20repackaged%20as%20welfare%20in%20its%20own%20programme.%20A%20well-articulated%20programme%20on%20education%2C%20health%20and%20employment%20could%20have%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-madhya-pradesh-rajasthan-chhattisgarh-bjp-congress-election%5C%22%3ETo%20Defeat%20BJP%20in%20an%20Increasingly%20Bipolar%20India%2C%20the%20Congress%20Would%20Need%20Much%20More%20Passion%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20the%20caste%20survey%20has%20not%20been%20implemented%20by%20any%20of%20the%20Congress-ruled%20states.%20Despite%20Bihar%20successfully%20carrying%20it%20out%2C%20it%20has%20not%20been%20fully%20adopted%20by%20the%20poll-bound%20states.%20Obviously%2C%20there%20are%20doubts%20on%20its%20national%20acceptability.%20The%20Congress%20has%20received%20imaginative%20suggestions%20from%20the%20Sachar%20Committee%20on%20building%20a%20diversity%20index%20and%20creating%20an%20Equal%20Opportunity%20Commission%2C%20but%20the%20party%20allowed%20it%20to%20be%20cold-storaged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20approval%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20the%20foremost%20national%20leader%20and%20the%20BJP%20ensconced%20comfortably%20in%20the%20north%20with%20a%20massive%20mandate%2C%20there%20is%20a%20steep%20uphill%20road%20ahead%20for%20not%20only%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20also%20for%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20it%20was%20hoping%20to%20lead.%20With%20the%20state%20parties%20having%20been%20pushed%20to%20the%20margins%20since%202014%20%E2%80%93%20until%20then%2C%20they%20had%20claimed%20one-third%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20%E2%80%93%20all%20the%20partners%20need%20to%20be%20humble%20and%20accommodative%2C%20a%20tough%20proposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Rahul%20has%20any%20desire%20to%20strengthen%20the%20alliance%2C%20he%20must%20be%20accommodative%20and%20make%20space.%20A%20programmatic%20agenda%20would%20have%20to%20predominate%20over%20criticisms%20of%20Modi.%20Institution-building%20must%20be%20forefronted%20with%20inclusive%20politics.%20Though%20the%20Congress%20is%20on%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20history%20for%202024%2C%20party%20building%20village%20by%20village%2C%20block%20by%20block%2C%20district%20by%20district%2C%20state%20by%20state%2C%20along%20with%20a%20massive%20political%20recruitment%20of%20the%20youth%2C%20could%20see%20a%20revival%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAjay%20K.%20Mehra%20was%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Senior%20Fellow%2C%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%202019-21.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702018843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08115047%2FScreenshot-2023-12-08-at-11.49.2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-narrative-polls-bjp-hindutva%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20three%20states%20lost%2C%20the%20Congress%20narrative%20was%20to%20ape%20the%20BJP.%20This%20won't%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongres