egends%20League%20Cricket%20(LLC)%20match%20on%20Wednesday.%20Both%20cricketers%20were%20part%20of%20the%202007%20T20%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%202011%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20winning%20squads%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20and%20their%20argument%20has%20resulted%20in%20some%20of%20their%20former%20colleagues%20weighing%20in%20on%20the%20topic.%20Gambhir%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20post%20an%20old%20picture%20of%20himself%20along%20with%20the%20caption%20-%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BSmile%20when%20the%20world%20is%20all%20about%20attention!%26quot%3B.%20Ex-%20India%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Irfan%20Pathan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F607-irfan-pathan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIrfan%20Pathan%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20quick%20to%20react%20to%20the%20picture%20as%20he%20wrote%20-%20%26quot%3BSmile%20is%20the%20best%20Answer%20brother.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESmile%20is%20the%20best%20Answer%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Irfan%20Pathan%20(%40IrfanPathan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIrfanPathan%2Fstatus%2F1732656887085273482%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreesanth%20alleged%20that%20ex-India%20teammate%20Gambhir%20called%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bfixer%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20World%20Cup-winning%20players%20were%20involved%20in%20a%20heated%20exchange%20during%20an%20Eliminator%20match%20between%20Indian%20Capitals%20and%20Gujarat%20Giants%20here%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20umpires%20had%20to%20intervene%20ad%20separate%20the%20two%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20kept%20on%20calling%20me%20'fixer%20fixer%2C%20you%20are%20a%20fixer%2C%20****%20off%20you%20fixer%20on%20live%20television%20on%20centre%20wicket%2C%26quot%3B%20Sreesanth%20said%20while%20going%20live%20from%20his%20Instagram%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20said%20'what%20are%20you%20saying'%2C%20I%20kept%20laughing%20in%20a%20sarcastic%20way.%20He%20spoke%20to%20the%20umpires%20in%20the%20same%20language%20when%20they%20tried%20to%20control%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESreesanth%20was%20handed%20a%20life%20ban%20by%20the%20BCCI's%20disciplinary%20committee%20due%20to%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20IPL%202013%20spot%20fixing%20scandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20ban%20was%20reduced%20to%20seven%20years%20in%202019%20by%20the%20Supreme%20court%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20my%20side%2C%20I%20didn't%20use%20any%20bad%20word.%20Please%20guys%20support%20the%20real%20truth.%20He%20has%20been%20doing%20it%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20why%20he%20started%20it%2C%20it%20was%20the%20end%20of%20the%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20his%20people%20are%20saying%20sixer%20sixer%20bola%20hai%20but%20unhone%20bola%20you%20fixer%2C%20tu%20fixer%20hai%20(his%20people%20are%20claiming%20he%20said%20sixer%20sixer%20but%20he%20said%20you%20are%20a%20fixer).%20This%20is%20not%20the%20way%20to%20talk.%20I'm%20thinking%20of%20leaving%20it%20(the%20incident)%20here%20but%20his%20people%20are%20trying%20to%20save%20him.%20I%20request%20you%20all%20to%20not%20fall%20for%20extra%20paid%20PR%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Sreesanth%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20hour%20after%20Sreesanth%20went%20live.%20Gambhir%2C%20who%20is%20a%20BJP%20MP%20from%20East%20Delhi%2C%20posted%20on%20X%20a%20picture%20of%20himself%20in%20the%20Indian%20jersey%20smiling%2C%20captioning%20it%20%26quot%3BSmile%20when%20the%20world%20is%20all%20about%20attention!%26quot%3B%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20in%20another%20Instagram%20live%20video%20after%20the%20game%20Sreesanth%20had%20called%20Gambhir%20%26quot%3BMr%20fighter%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20did%20not%20even%20respect%20senior%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20wanted%20to%20clear%20the%20air%20with%20what%20happened%20with%20Mr%20fighter.%20One%20who%20always%20fights%20with%20all%20his%20colleagues.%20For%20no%20reason%20whatsoever.%20He%20does%20not%20even%20respect%20his%20own%20senior%20players%2C%20including%20Viru%20Bahi%20(%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virender%20Sehwag%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F86-virender-sehwag-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirender%20Sehwag%3C%2Fa%3E)%20%26quot%3BThat's%20exactly%20what%20happened%20today.%20Without%20any%20provocation%2C%20he%20just%20kept%20on%20calling%20me%20something%20which%20was%20very%20rude%20which%20shouldn't%20have%20been%20said%20by%20Mr%20Gautam%20Gambhir%2C%26quot%3B%20Sreesanth%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20at%20all%20at%20fault%20here.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20clear%20the%20air%20straight%20away.%20What%20Mr%20Gauti%20has%20done%2C%20sooner%20or%20later%20all%20of%20you%20will%20get%20to%20know.%20The%20words%20that%20he%20used%20and%20the%20things%20he%20said%20on%20a%20cricket%20field%2C%20live%2C%20is%20not%20acceptable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20family%2C%20my%20state%2C%20everybody%20has%20gone%20through%20so%20much.%20I%20fought%20that%20battle%20with%20all%20your%20support.%20Now%20people%20want%20to%20down%20me%20for%20no%20reason.%20He%20said%20things%20he%20shouldn't%20have%20said.%20I%20will%20surely%20let%20you%20know%20what%20he%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20reiterated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Gambhir%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20an%20on%20field%20altercation.%20He%20has%20had%20fiery%20exchanges%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20during%20the%20IPL%2C%20including%20earlier%20this%20year%20when%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%20took%20on%20Lucknow%20S