arvard%20antisemitism%20adviser%20quits%20after%20university%20head%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98painful%E2%80%99%20hearing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702013343000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105829843%2Cimgsize-220360.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frabbi-david-wolpe-harvard-antisemitism-adviser-quits-after-university-heads-painful-hearing%2Farticleshow%2F105829798.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105829798.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERabbi%20David%20Wolpe%20resigned%20from%20Harvard%20University's%20antisemitism%20advisory%20committee%20due%20to%20concerns%20over%20rising%20antisemitism%20on%20campus.%20Wolpe%2C%20a%20visiting%20scholar%20at%20Harvard%20Divinity%20School%2C%20cited%20events%20on%20campus%20and%20President%20Claudine%20Gay's%20inadequate%20testimony%20at%20a%20congressional%20hearing%20as%20reasons%20for%20his%20decision.%20Wolpe%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20acknowledging%20the%20Jewish%20experience%20and%20criticized%20the%20narrow%20legal%20responses%20from%20Gay%20and%20other%20university%20leaders%20regarding%20the%20issue%20of%20calling%20for%20the%20genocide%20of%20Jews.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frabbi-david-wolpe-harvard-antisemitism-adviser-quits-after-university-heads-painful-hearing%2Farticleshow%2F105829798.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reserve%20Bank%20Of%20India%20Keeps%20Key%20Lending%20Rate%20Unchanged%20At%206.5%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India's%20key%20lending%20rate%20was%20held%20steady%20at%20at%206.5%20per%20cent%2C%20RBI%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20announced%20today.%20The%20monetary%20policy%20committee%20took%20the%20decision%20with%20inflation%20control%20remaining%20a%20major%20focus%20amid%20expectations%20of%20a%20spike%20in%20food%20prices%20in%20coming%20months%20and%20better%20than%20expected%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20monetary%20policy%20kept%20the%20repo%20rate%2C%20a%20key%20lending%20rate%2C%20unchanged%20for%20the%20fifth%20consecutive%20time.%20The%20repo%20rate%20is%20the%20rate%20of%20interest%20at%20which%20RBI%20lends%20to%20other%20banks.%20This%20means%20the%20loan%20interest%20rates%20too%20are%20likely%20to%20remain%20unchanged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERBI%20also%20raised%20the%20UPI%20payment%20limits%20for%20hospitals%20and%20educational%20institutions%20to%20Rs%205%20lakh%20from%20Rs%201%20lakh%20per%20transaction%2C%20Mr%20Das%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERBI%20Governor%20said%20the%20global%20economy%20is%20showing%20signs%20of%20economy%20and%20said%20while%20the%20headline%20inflation%20receded%20from%20last%20year%2C%20it%20remains%20above%20target%20in%20many%20countries%20and%20core%20inflation%20continues%20to%20remain%20sticky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20economy%20presents%20picture%20of%20resilience%20and%20momentum%2C%20Mr%20Das%20said%2C%20emphasising%20that%20Q2%20GDP%20exceeded%20all%20forecasts%20and%20fiscal%20consolidation%20is%20on%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExternal%20balance%20remaining%20eminently%20manageable%2C%20the%20central%20banker%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20the%20RBI's%20endeavour%20to%20further%20build%20on%20these%20fundamentals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Nifty%20reached%2021%2C000%20for%20the%20first%20time%20as%20the%20RBI's%20Monetary%20Policy%20Committee%20held%20the%20key%20rate%20unchanged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20also%20maintained%20its%20policy%20stance%20of%20%26quot%3Bwithdrawal%20of%20accommodation%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20inflation%20progressively%20aligns%20with%20the%20committee's%20target%20while%20remaining%20supportive%20of%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20has%20projected%20retail%20inflation%20at%205.4%20per%20cent%20for%20Financial%20Year%202024%2C%20Mr%20Das%20said.%20RBI%20projected%20real%20GDP%20growth%20for%20the%202023-24%20fiscal%20at%207%20per%20cent%2C%20with%20December%20and%20March%20quarter%20growth%20estimated%20at%206.5%20per%20cent%20and%206%20per%20cent%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20had%20raised%20the%20repo%20rate%20by%20a%20total%20250%20basis%20points%20(bps)%20since%20May%202022%20in%20efforts%20to%20cool%20surging%20inflation%2C%20which%20dropped%20to%20a%20four-month%20low%20of%204.87%25%20in%20October%2C%20but%20is%20expected%20to%20remain%20above%20the%20RBI's%204%25%20medium-term%20target%20for%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20economy%20grew%207.6%25%20in%20the%20July-September%20quarter%2C%20much%20faster%20than%20the%20polled%20median%20of%206.8%25%20and%20RBI's%20estimate%20of%206.5%25%2C%20helped%20by%20government%20spending%20and%20manufacturing%2C%20raising%20bets%20that%20Asia's%20third-largest%20economy%20will%20outperform%20its%20own%20estimates%20for%20the%20full%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702013160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fe1esg0lg_shaktikanta-das_625x300_13_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freserve-bank-of-india-keeps-key-lending-rate-unchanged-at-6-5-4644628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India's%20Monetary%20Policy%20Committee%20unanimously%20kept%20the%20key%20lending%20rate%20unchanged%20at%206.5%20per%20cent%2C%20RBI%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20announced%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freserve-bank-of-india-keeps-key-lending-rate-unchanged-at-6-5-4644628%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freserve-bank-of-india-keeps-key-lending-rate-unchanged-at-6-5-4644628%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Freserve-bank-of-india-keeps-key-lending-rate-unchanged-at-6-5-4644628%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Qatar%3A%20Indian%20ambassador%20meets%20eight%20ex-naval%20officers%20on%20death%20row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702013104000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F336D%2Fproduction%2F_131956131_gettyimages-1297070538.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67656682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Media%20reports%20say%20the%20men%20have%20been%20charged%20with%20spying%2C%20but%20India%20and%20Qatar%20have%20not%20confirmed%20this.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67656682%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67656682.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-67656682.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20War%20Without%20the%20Fig%20Leaf%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07231211%2FIsrael_Supreme_Court.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20war%20in%20Gaza%20continues%2C%20and%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20wars%20in%20many%20decades%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%20is%20not%20in%20the%20picture%2C%20not%20even%20in%20appearance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20few%20petitions%20submitted%20by%20human%20rights%20organisations%20were%20also%20rejected%3A%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.acri.org.il%2Fpost%2F__987%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epetition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20dema