Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20the%20title%20%E2%80%9CThe%20political%2C%20military%20and%20legal%20echelons%20managed%20to%20join%20hands%20in%20the%20war%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMinister%20of%20Justice%20Yariv%20Levin%20unintentionally%20helped%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%20to%20emphasise%20to%20the%20Israeli%20public%20its%20patriotism%2C%20non-interference%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20and%20in%20security%20matters%20in%20general.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20happened%20when%20Minister%20Levin%20falsely%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.now14.co.il%2F%25D7%259C%25D7%2595%25D7%2599%25D7%259F-%25D7%25A6%25D7%25A8%25D7%2599%25D7%259A-%25D7%25A9%25D7%2599%25D7%25A0%25D7%2595%25D7%2599-%25D7%2592%25D7%2599%25D7%25A9%25D7%2594-%25D7%2591%25D7%259E%25D7%25A2%25D7%25A8%25D7%259B%25D7%25AA-%25D7%2594%25D7%259E%25D7%25A9%25D7%25A4%25D7%2598-%25D7%2591%25D7%2599%25D7%259F%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20the%20right%20wing%20Channel%2014%20that%20the%20judges%20of%20the%20Court%20%E2%80%9Ctied%20our%20hands%20in%20ability%20to%20fight%E2%80%9D%20when%20they%20determined%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20impossible%20to%20shoot%20anyone%20approaching%20the%20fence%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20he%20tried%20to%20accuse%20the%20judges%20of%20being%20responsible%20for%20the%20massacres%20and%20kidnappings%20committed%20by%20Hamas%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fkidnapping-civilians-from-israel-hamas-war-crime%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOctober%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20courts%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ynet.co.il%2Fnews%2Farticle%2Fbjtwcvd4a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eresponded%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%202018%2C%20following%20violent%20events%20that%20took%20place%20near%20the%20perimeter%20fence%20on%20the%20border%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20a%20petition%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%20in%20which%20it%20was%20claimed%20that%20the%20IDF%E2%80%99s%20rules%20of%20engagement%2C%20which%20includes%20live%20fire%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20is%20illegal.%20The%20petition%20was%20rejected%20unanimously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Court%20noted%20in%20the%20ruling%20that%20the%20scope%20of%20its%20intervention%20in%20issues%20of%20this%20kind%20is%20limited%20and%20extremely%20narrow%2C%20and%20in%20any%20case%2C%20there%20is%20no%20basis%20for%20the%20claim%20that%20the%20rules%20of%20engagement%20were%20changed%20due%20to%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%E2%80%99s%20ruling.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20the%20response%20of%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20courts%20it%20may%20be%20implied%20that%20the%20judges%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%20approved%20the%20content%20of%20IDF%E2%80%99s%20rules%20of%20engagement%2C%20but%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20the%20they%20did%20not%20even%20read%20at%20the%20confidential%20rules%20and%20the%20additional%20confidential%20material%20since%20the%20petitioners%20objected%20to%20this%20(this%20is%20stated%20in%20section%2025%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nevo.co.il%2Fpsika_html%2Felyon%2F18030030-K08.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eruling%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContrary%20to%20the%20claims%20of%20Minister%20Levin%20and%20other%20supporters%20in%20Israel%20of%20reducing%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20real%20protection%20of%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20the%20court%20has%20never%20really%20been%20an%20address%2C%20and%20except%20in%20rare%20cases%20its%20judges%20have%20generally%20refrained%20from%20interfering%20in%20the%20decisions%20of%20the%20security%20establishment%20and%20the%20government.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20the%20court%20did%20serve%20as%20an%20effective%20fig%20leaf.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20telegram%20dated%20January%2025%2C%201993%2C%20sent%20by%20an%20Israeli%20envoy%20in%20London%2C%20Gideon%20Meir%2C%20to%20the%20deputy%20director%20of%20the%20European%20region%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20in%20Israel%2C%20reveals%20how%20the%20fig%20leaf%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%20worked%20in%20practice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeir%20informed%20that%20he%20met%20with%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20region%20at%20the%20British%20Foreign%20Office%2C%20and%20that%20the%20Americans%20and%20the%20British%20are%20acting%20on%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20request%20to%20postpone%20a%20discussion%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20(UNSC)%2C%20before%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%E2%80%99s%20decision%20on%20the%20petitions%20filed%20by%20the%20Association%20for%20Civil%20Rights%20in%20Israel%20and%20others%20against%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20forced%20deportation%20of%20Hamas%20militants%20to%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20British%20diplomat%20explained%20that%20they%20were%20able%20to%20postpone%20the%20discussion%20in%20the%20UNSC%20and%20that%20Britain%20sees%20three%20possible%20scenarios%20following%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%20ruling%3A%20a%20decision%20regarding%20the%20illegality%20of%20the%20deportation%20that%20will%20resolve%20the%20problem%2C%20a%20decision%20regarding%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20deportation%20with%20different%20interpretations%20that%20will%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20the%20Israeli%20government%20to%20change%20direction%2C%20and%20a%20decision%20that%20will%20confirm%20unequivocally%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20deportation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20British%20diplomat%20explained%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20last%20two%20scenarios%2C%20he%20assumes%20that%20it%20will%20not%20be%20possible%20to%20prevent%20an%20immediate%20meeting%20of%20the%20UNSC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeir%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20the%20British%20diplomat%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20amazing%2C%20since%20even%20though%20he%20represented%20a%20government%20that%20was%20fighting%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%20for%20the%20legality%20of%20its%20position%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20even%20if%20there%20is%20indeed%20an%20unequivocal%20decision%20by%20the%20court%20supporting%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20deportation%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20would%20be%20better%20to%20allow%20an%20additional%20waiting%20period%20to%20allow%20the%20parties%20to%20rethink%20their%20steps.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20is%2C%20while%20one%20hand%20of%20the%20government%20was%20fighting%20in%20the%20court%20to%20defend%20its%20position%20and%20dismiss%20the%20petitions%2C%20the%20other%20hand%20used%20the%20court%20and%20petitions%20for%20diplomatic%20purposes%20and%20also%20tried%20to%20use%20the%20possible%20rulings%20as%20a%20ladder%20to%20get%20off%20the%20tree.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Israeli%20government%20did%20%E2%80%9Chorse-trading%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20UNSC%20through%20the%20fig%20leaf%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETime%20will%20tell%20if%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20current%20war%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20continuation%20of%20the%20occupation%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20without%20the%20fig%20leaf%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%20will%20pay%20off%20for%20Israel%20and%20not%20only%20hasten%20the%20arrival%20of%20Israelis%20as%20defendants%20at%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20in%20The%20Hague.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20it%20is%20not%20certain%20that%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20fig%20leaf%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20of%20Justice%20will%20help%20them%2C%20as%20the%20Israel%20has%20additional%20tools%20to%20prevent%20their%20success%20in%20promoting%20proceedings%20and%20justice%20in%20international%20courts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EEitay%20Mack%20is%20an%20Israeli%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20and%20activist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the7eye.org.il%2F503747%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Earticle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0first%20appeared%20on%20the%20Hebrew%20media%20platform%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the7eye.org.il%2Fabout%2Fenglish%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Seventh%20Eye%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702013096000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07231211%2FIsrael_Supreme_Court.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fa-war-without-the-fig-leaf-of-the-high-court-of-justice%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Time%20will%20tell%20if%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20current%20war%20in%20Gaza%20without%20a%20cover%20from%20its%20top%20court%20will%20pay%20off%20for%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fa-war-without-the-fig-leaf-of-the-high-court-of-justice%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UPI%20transaction%20limits%20hiked%2C%20new%20rules%20for%20recurring%20payments%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702012501000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105830275%2Cimgsize-33212.cms