y%20of%20the%20first%20coram%20is%20also%20being%20ignored%20in%20doing%20so.%20Our%20attention%20is%20also%20been%20drawn%20by%20esteemed%20Colleagues%20at%20the%20Bar%2C%20Seniors%2C%20and%20Advocates%20on%20Record%20(AoRs)%2C%20about%20various%20cases%20in%20which%20they%20have%20appeared%20in%20the%20first%20instance%20on%20numerous%20occasions%2C%20later%20the%20matters%20being%20listed%20before%20different%20Benches.%20It%20would%20not%20be%20proper%20for%20me%20to%20enumerate%20these%20matters%20as%20many%20of%20them%20are%20pending%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Bar%20Association%20has%20also%20written%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud%2C%20expressing%20%E2%80%9Cfull%20faith%20and%20confidence%20in%20the%20neutrality%20and%20unprecedent%20administrative%20skill%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20CJI.%20The%20letter%20was%20signed%20by%20president%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Bar%20Association%2C%20Adish%20C.%20Aggarwala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Bar%20has%20full%20faith%20and%20reposes%20full%20confidence%20in%20the%20neutrality%20and%20unprecedented%20administrative%20skill%20of%20Your%20Lordship%20and%20other%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20companion%20Judges%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20the%20administration%20of%20justice.%20It%20is%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20that%20the%20last%20person%20standing%20in%20the%20queue%20has%20also%20been%20given%20equal%20and%20full%20access%20to%20justice.%20After%20Your%20Lordship%20took%20over%20as%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20all%20administrative%20issues%20have%20been%20streamlined%20right%20from%20mentioning%20of%20matters%2C%20listing%20of%20cases%20and%20other%20issues%20concerning%20the%20Registry%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20stated%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fday-after-dave-letter-sc-bar-body-reposes-full-faith-in-cji%2Fa