s%2C%E2%80%9D%20Johnson%20said%C2%A0under%20oath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98We%20got%20some%20things%20wrong%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%E2%80%99s%20Health%20Secretary%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fuk-health-secretary-hancock-quits-after-being-filmed-kissing-aide%2Fa-58058627%5C%22%3EMatt%20Hancock%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20the%20inquiry%20last%20week%20that%20he%20had%20tried%20to%20raise%20the%20alarm%20inside%20the%20government%2C%20saying%20thousands%20of%20lives%20could%20have%20been%20saved%20by%20putting%20the%20country%20into%20lockdown%20a%20few%20weeks%20earlier%20than%20the%20eventual%20date%20of%20March%2023%2C%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInevitably%20we%20got%20some%20things%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20Johnson%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20took%20personal%20responsibility%20for%20all%20the%20decisions%20made.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20we%20were%20doing%20our%20best%20in%20very%20difficult%20circumstances%E2%80%A6%20we%20underestimated%20the%20scale%20and%20the%20pace%20of%20the%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%2C%20who%20was%20prime%20minister%20from%202019%20to%202022%2C%C2%A0was%20briefly%20interrupted%20when%20a%20protester%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20inquiry%20room%20in%20London%20after%20refusing%20to%20be%20seated%20during%20Johnson%E2%80%99s%20apology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20others%20were%20also%20later%20removed%2C%20shouting%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dead%20can%E2%80%99t%20hear%20your%20apologies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMissing%20WhatsApp%20messages%2C%20soaring%20death%20toll%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%20arrived%20three%20hours%20early%20for%20the%20hearing%2C%20suggesting%20an%20attempt%C2%A0to%20avoid%20the%20bereaved%20families%2C%20some%20of%C2%A0whom%20assembled%20outside%20Dorland%20House%20in%20west%20London%20throughout%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fuk-covid-deaths-pass-150000-amid-omicron-surge%2Fa-60370443%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20230%2C000%20people%20died%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0after%20contracting%20COVID-19%20in%20the%20UK%20between%20March%202020%20and%20mid-July%202021%2C%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20per%20capita%20tolls%20among%20Western%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaced%20with%20evidence%20by%20inquiry%20counsel%20Hugo%20Keith%20that%20the%20UK%20fared%20worse%20in%20the%20pandemic%20than%20its%20European%20neighbors%2C%20Johnson%20argued%20that%20%E2%80%9Cevery%20country%20struggled%20with%20a%20new%20pandemic%E2%80%9D%20while%20noting%20the%20UK%20had%20an%20%E2%80%9Cextremely%20elderly%20population%E2%80%9D%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20continent%E2%80%99s%20most%20densely%20populated%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%E2%80%99s%20grilling%20began%20with%20questions%20about%20a%20failure%20to%20provide%20about%205%2C000%20WhatsApp%20messages%20on%20his%20phone%20from%20late%20January%202020%20to%20June%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20exact%20reason%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed%2C%20adding%20the%20app%20had%20%E2%80%9Csomehow%E2%80%9D%20automatically%20erased%20its%20chat%20history%20from%20that%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20had%20initiated%20a%20so-called%20factory%20reset%20of%20a%20mobile%20device%2C%20Johnson%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20remember%20any%20such%20thing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EJohnson%20%E2%80%98bamboozled%E2%80%99%20by%20data%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%2C%20who%20agreed%20to%20hold%20a%20COVID-19%20inquiry%20in%20late%202021%20following%20pressure%20from%20the%20families%20of%20the%20bereaved%2C%20was%20accused%20by%20former%20aides%20of%20indecisiveness%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20scientific%20understanding%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20former%20chief%20scientific%20officer%2C%20Patrick%20Vallance%2C%20said%20Johnson%20was%20frequently%20%E2%80%9Cbamboozled%E2%80%9D%20by%20scientific%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%E2%80%99s%20former%20adviser%20Dominic%20Cummings%2C%20now%20a%20fierce%20opponent%20of%20Johnson%2C%20said%20the%20then-prime%20minister%20asked%20scientists%20whether%20blowing%20a%20hair%20dryer%20up%20his%20nose%20could%20kill%20the%20virus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ex-leader%20has%20also%20denied%20claims%20he%20said%20he%20would%20rather%20%E2%80%9Clet%20the%20bodies%20pile%20high%E2%80%9D%20than%20impose%20another%20lockdown%2C%20comments%20he%20denies%20ever%20having%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrent%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fwho-is-britains-next-prime-minister-rishi-sunak%2Fa-52375317%5C%22%3ERishi%20Sunak%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20Johnson%E2%80%99s%20Chancellor%20(finance%20minister)%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20is%20due%20to%20be%20questioned%20at%20the%20inquiry%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fboris-johnson-apologizes-to-uk-covid-victims%2Fa-67647936%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3C%2Fi%3EDW.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702009008000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08023931%2FBoris_Johnson_GOV_UK.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fboris-johnson-apologises-to-uk-covid-victims%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Boris%20Johnson%20said%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20sorry%20for%20the%20pain%20and%20suffering%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20UK's%20COVID-19%20victims.%20While%20he%20admitted%20to%20making%20mistakes%2C%20he%20defended%20his%20record%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fboris-johnson-apologises-to-uk-covid-victims%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20Demands%20Sacking%20Of%20Disney%20CEO%20Bob%20Iger.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20is%20demanding%20the%20firing%20of%20Disney%20CEO%20Bob%20Iger%20in%20response%20to%20Disney's%20decision%20to%20pull%20advertisements%20from%20his%20troubled%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20X%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Musk%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20X%20and%20a%20billionaire%20conspiracy%20theorist%2C%20took%20to%20social%20media%2C%20where%20he%20frequently%20voices%20his%20opinions%2C%20to%20express%20his%20discontent%20with%20Iger's%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Musk%2C%20known%20for%20using%20his%20influential%20platform%20to%20confront%20critics%2C%20declared%20that%20Iger%20should%20be%20immediately%20ousted%20from%20his%20role%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20should%20be%20fired%20immediately.%20Walt%20Disney%20is%20turning%20in%20his%20grave%20over%20what%20Bob%20has%20done%20to%20his%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Disney%20have%20not%20yet%20responded%20to%20Mr%20Musk's%20call%20for%20Iger's%20termination.%20Iger%20is%20widely%20acknowledged%20for%20steering%20Disney%20to%20entertainment%20dominance%20through%20strategic%20acquisitions%2C%20including%20Star%20Wars%2C%20Marvel%20Studios%2C%20and%20Pixar%2C%20according%20to%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisney%2C%20like%20several%20other%20major%20companies%2C%20halted%20advertising%20on%20X%20last%20month%20after%20Mr%20Musk%20endorsed%20an%20anti-Semitic%20conspiracy%20theory%20favoured%20by%20White%20supremacists.%20Mr%20Musk%20offered%20a%20tacit%20apology%20for%20the%20post%20last%20week%20but%20simultaneously%20delivered%20a%20profanity-laced%20message%20to%20companies%20choosing%20to%20avoid%20advertising%20on%20his%20social%20media%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20DealBook%20Summit%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20directed%20his%20ire%20at%20Iger%2C%20criticising%20the%20Disney%20CEO%20for%20the%20decision%20to%20cease%20advertising%20on%20X%2C%20citing%20Musk%20as%20the%20reason.%20Iger%20explained%20that%20the%20association%20with%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20X%20was%20not%20seen%20as%20positive%20for%20Disney.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20felt%20that%20the%20association%20with...%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20X%20was%20not%20necessarily%20a%20positive%20one%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20CNN%20quoted%20Iger%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20stop%20advertisements%20coincides%20with%20a%20broader%20trend%20on%20X%20since%20Mr%20Musk%20assumed%20control%20in%20late%202022.%20His%20decisions%20have%20contributed%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20hate%20speech%2C%20misinformation%2C%20and%20conspiracy%20theories%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CNN%20report%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20himself%20has%20played%20a%20role%20in%20fostering%20toxicity%20on%20X%2C%20including%20promoting%20the%20false%20and%20dangerous%20Pizzagate%20conspiracy%20theory.%20The%20lack%20of%20major%20advertising%20partners%20has%20severely%20impacted%20X's%20finances%2C%20as%20the%20platform%20relies%20heavily%20on%20advertising%20revenue.%20Mr%20Musk%20admitted%20at%20the%20DealBook%20Summit%20that%20the%20ongoing%20advertising%20boycott%20is%20likely%20to%20lead%20to%20the%20demise%20of%20his%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20this%20advertising%20boycott%20is%20going%20to%20do%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20kill%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20Elon%20Musk%20candidly%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20financial%20challenges%20faced%20by%20X%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20has%20not%20taken%20personal%20responsibility%20for%20the%20situation%2C%20deflecting%20blame%20onto%20advertisers%20and%20suggesting%20they%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20potential%20downfall%20of%20X%2C%20CNN%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20sy