Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20tweet%20of%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20of%20Mauritius%2C%20the%20participants%20included%20the%20National%20Security%20Advisors%20of%20India%2C%20Mauritius%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20as%20well%20as%20delegates%20from%20Seychelles%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaldives%2C%20which%20recently%20witnessed%20a%20change%20in%20government%20after%20the%20presidential%20election%2C%20was%20missing%20on%20the%20list%20posted%20by%20the%20high%20commission.%20It%20remains%20unclear%20whether%20the%20Maldives%20had%20representation%20at%20a%20lower%20level%20or%20the%20country%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20meeting%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20highlighted%20that%20NSA%20Doval%20underscored%20the%20pivotal%20role%20of%20the%20CSC%20in%20guaranteeing%20regional%20security%20and%20stability.%20He%20also%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20sustained%20engagement%20across%20various%20pillars%20of%20cooperation%20%E2%80%9CMembers%20also%20agreed%20on%20a%20Roadmap%20of%20Activities%20for%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20his%20statement%2C%20NSA%20Shri%20Ajit%20Doval%20emphasised%20the%20crucial%20role%20of%20CSC%20in%20ensuring%20regional%20security%20%26amp%3B%20stability%2C%20and%20highlighted%20the%20significance%20of%20continued%20engagements%20under%20the%20different%20pillars%20of%20cooperation.%20Members%20also%20agreed%20on%20a%20Roadmap%20of%20Activities%20for%202024.%20(2%2F2)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20India%20in%20Mauritius%20(%40HCI_PortLouis)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHCI_PortLouis%2Fstatus%2F1732684450591588668%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20pillars%20of%20cooperation%20within%20the%20CSC%20encompass%20maritime%20safety%20and%20security%2C%20counterterrorism%20and%20counter-radicalisation%20initiatives%2C%20the%20combat%20against%20trafficking%20and%20transnational%20organised%20crime%2C%20cybersecurity%20and%20protection%20of%20critical%20infrastructure%2C%20as%20well%20as%20humanitarian%20assistance%20and%20disaster%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20three%20countries%20met%20after%20six%20years%20in%202020%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20201220035314%2Fhttps%3A%2Fthewire.in%2Fexternal-affairs%2Findia-maldives-sri-lanka-trilateral-initiative%5C%22%3Ethey%20agreed%20to%20expand%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20membership%20of%20the%20trilateral%20grouping.%20Mauritius%20joined%20the%20revived%20Colombo%20Security%20Conclave%20in%20March%202022%2C%20while%20Bangladesh%20and%20Seychelles%20have%20been%20taken%20part%20in%20the%20meetings%20as%20observers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaldives%20vice-president%20Hussain%20Mohamed%20Latheef%20is%20currently%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20Kunming%20to%20attend%20the%20%E2%80%98China-Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20Forum%20on%20Development%20Cooperation%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702008442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F08093554%2FGAvCXplbwAAhh3_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnsa-ajit-doval-underlines-importance-of-colombo-security-conclave-co-founder-maldives-skips-meeting%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20sixth%20meeting%20of%20the%20Colombo%20Security%20Conclave%2C%20founded%20by%20India%2C%20Maldives%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%202011%2C%20was%20held%20at%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20nation%20of%20Mauritius%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnsa-ajit-doval-underlines-importance-of-colombo-security-conclave-co-founder-maldives-skips-meeting%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22T