exploring%20options%20to%20ensure%20that%20students%20find%20adequate%20housing.%20These%20long-overdue%20changes%20will%20protect%20international%20students%20from%20financially%20vulnerable%20situations%20and%20exploitation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Miller.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20the%20cost-of-living%20requirement%20has%20remained%20stagnant%20at%20USD%2010%2C000%20for%20a%20single%20applicant.%20However%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20evolving%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20the%20threshold%20will%20now%20be%20raised%20to%20USD%2020%2C635%2C%20representing%2075%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20low-income%20cut-off%20(LICO).%20This%20adjustment%2C%20to%20be%20updated%20annually%20with%20Statistics%20Canada's%20LICO%2C%20aims%20to%20ensure%20that%20international%20students%20are%20adequately%20prepared%20for%20the%20financial%20demands%20of%20life%20in%20Canada%2C%20the%20release%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20is%20not%20only%20a%20response%20to%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20living%20but%20also%20addresses%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20international%20students%2C%20such%20as%20finding%20suitable%20housing.%20The%20reforms%20align%20with%20the%20government's%20commitment%20to%20protecting%20students%20from%20financial%20vulnerability%20and%20exploitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20support%20underrepresented%20cohorts%20of%20international%20students%2C%20the%20government%20plans%20to%20implement%20targeted%20pilots%20in%20collaboration%20with%20partners%20in%202024.%20These%20pilots%20will%20test%20new%20ideas%20to%20facilitate%20the%20pursuit%20of%20studies%20in%20Canada%20for%20students%20facing%20unique%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20follows%20the%20October%2027%2C%202023%2C%20reforms%20to%20the%20International%20Student%20Programme%2C%20introducing%20a%20new%20framework%20to%20recognise%20learning%20institutions%20providing%20top-quality%20services%20and%20support%2C%20including%20housing.%20Learni