not%20shared%20%E2%80%9Csubstantive%E2%80%9D%20evidence%20and%20therefore%2C%20there%20was%20no%20similar%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2029%2C%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20have%20accused%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20of%20collaborating%20with%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20in%20a%20thwarted%20scheme%20to%20assassinate%20Sikh%20separatist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20a%20dual%20citizen%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Canada.%20India%20had%20said%20that%20it%20was%20taking%20the%20matter%20seriously%20and%20had%20constituted%20a%20high-level%20committee%20of%20enquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20earlier%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20announced%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20parliament%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Cpotential%E2%80%9D%20links%20of%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20leader%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20on%20Canadian%20soil%20in%20June.%20It%20triggered%20an%20angry%20reaction%20from%20India%2C%20resulting%20in%20recall%20of%2041%20Canadian%20diplomats%20and%20stopping%20of%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadian%20nationals%2C%20which%20has%20since%20been%20resumed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInsofar%20as%20the%20US%20is%20concerned%2C%20certain%20inputs%20were%20given%20to%20us%20as%20part%20of%20our%20security%20cooperation%20with%20the%20United%20States.%20Those%20inputs%20were%20of%20concern%20to%20us%20because%20they%20%5Bwere%5D%20related%20to%20the%20nexus%20of%20organised%20crime%2C%20trafficking%20and%20other%20matters%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20mentioned%20that%20due%20to%20the%20inputs%E2%80%99%20impact%20on%20national%20security%2C%20a%20decision%20had%20been%20made%20to%20constitute%20an%20inquiry%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20indictment%20filed%20in%20a%20New%20York%20court%20had%20also%20linked%20the%20unnamed%20Indian%20government%20official%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20why%20India%20had%20not%20made%20similar%20response%20to%20Canadian%20charges%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CInsofar%20as%20Canada%20is%20concerned%2C%20no%20specific%20evidence%20or%20inputs%20were%20provided%20to%20us.%20So%20the%20question%20of%20equitable%20treatment%20to%20two%20countries%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20has%20provided%20input%20and%20one%20of%20whom%20has%20not%2C%20does%20not%20arise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20weekly%20briefing%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20the%20upcoming%20visit%20of%20the%20director%20of%20the%20US%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20Christopher%20Wray%2C%20had%20been%20planned%20for%20the%20last%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20you%20are%20aware%2C%20we%20have%20robust%20security%2C%20cyber%20security%2C%20counter-terrorism%20and%20counter-narcotics%20cooperation%20with%20the%20US%20agencies%2C%20we%20also%20engage%20in%20capacity%20building%20programs.%20So%20as%20part%20of%20this%20ongoing%20bilateral%20cooperation%2C%20visit%20by%20the%20FBI%20director%20is%20in%20the%20works%2C%20is%20being%20held%2C%20but%20let%20them%20confirm%20the%20exact%20things.%20Details%20of%20this%20visit%20have%20been%20worked%20out%20with%20the%20US%20side%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20last%20few%20months%20and%20as%20I%20said%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20confirm%20the%20specific%20timeline%20for%20that%2C%20that%20I%20would%20leave%20to%20the%20US%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20another%20question%20whether%20Pannun%20case%20will%20be%20discussed%20during%20Wray%E2%80%99s%20trip%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20dialogue%20process.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20crystal%20ball%2C%20so%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20guess%20into%20what%20may%20or%20may%20not%20be%20discussed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%