t%20format%20of%20the%20game%3F%20Since%20India's%20defeat%20in%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup%20semi-final%20against%20England%2C%20the%2035-year-old%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%2036%2C%20have%20not%20played%20T20Is.%20Their%20absence%2C%20rather%20than%20causing%20a%20void%2C%20has%20been%20filled%20by%20a%20crop%20of%20young%20talent%20which%20coincided%20with%20a%20series%20of%20victories%20for%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20India%20clinched%20a%20three-match%20series%20in%20New%20Zealand%20late%20last%20year%2C%20secured%20the%20gold%20medal%20at%20the%20Asian%20Games%20and%20recently%20registered%20a%204-1%20series%20win%20over%20Australia.%20The%20youngsters%20have%20also%20helped%20India%20solidify%20their%20position%20as%20the%20top-ranked%20team%20in%20the%20format.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20and%20Sharma's%20credentials%20are%20impeccable%20and%20their%20track%20record%20certainly%20makes%20a%20case%20for%20their%20inclusion%20in%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20West%20Indies.%20However%2C%20the%20Indian%20team%20has%20handed%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20T20I%20debuts%20since%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Among%20these%20fresh%20faces%2C%20the%20emergence%20of%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%2C%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan%2C%20Rinku%20Singh%2C%20and%20Tilak%20Varma%20has%20been%20nothing%20but%20exceptional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20young%20guns%2C%20all%20aged%2026%20or%20below%2C%20have%20proven%20themselves%20worthy%20of%20regular%20places%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%20and%20not%20just%20a%20few%20sporadic%20appearances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERinku%20Singh%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20looks%20ready%20to%20take%20on%20the%20role%20of%20a%20finisher.%20The%2026-year-old%20played%20three%20cameos%20in%20differing%20situations%20in%20the%20series%20against%20Australia.%20He%20took%20the%20team%20over%20the%20line%20with%20a%20last-ball%20six%20in%20the%20first%20T20I%20before%20helping%20the%20team%20register%20235%20in%20the%20second%20T20I%20by%20striking%2031%20off%209.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpeners%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20enabled%20India%20to%20register%20strong%20starts%20in%20the%20series.%20Gaikwad%2C%20with%20223%20runs%2C%20was%20the%20leading%20run-scorer%20in%20the%20series%20while%20Jaiswal%20scored%20138%20runs%20at%20the%20top.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIshan%20Kishan%20and%20Tilak%20Varma%20have%20also%20been%20among%20the%20runs%20this%20year%20and%20played%20crucial%20knocks%20in%20the%20middle%20order%20in%20both%20domestic%20and%20international%20competitions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20gears%20up%20for%20the%20impending%20tour%20to%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20inclusion%20of%20these%20young%20guns%20in%20the%20white-ball%20squad%20along%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Sai%20Sudharsan%20%E2%80%94%20who%20impressed%20in%20the%20IPL%20representing%20Gujarat%20Titans%20%E2%80%94%20underscores%20a%20shift%20in%20the%20team's%20dynamics.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20will%20play%20only%20in%20the%20Test%20series%2C%20giving%20the%20impression%20that%20Indian%20selectors%20are%20ready%20to%20alter%20the%20complexion%20of%20India's%20squad%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad%20next%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20temptation%20to%20build%20something%20resembling%20MS%20Dhoni's%20young%20side%20that%20managed%20to%20achieve%20in%20the%202007%20T20%20World%20Cup%20is%20understandable%2C%20the%20balance%20between%20experience%20and%20youth%20remains%20crucial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20were%20the%20leading%20run-scorers%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20and%20their%20presence%20on%20the%20pitch%20still%20hands%20India%20a%20massive%20psychological%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20captain%20scored%20597%20runs%20in%20the%20World%20Cup