eeds.%20I%20have%20an%20active%20dog%20who%20frequently%20goes%20swimming%20and%20hiking%20with%20me%20in%20our%20city's%20parks%20and%20recreation%20areas%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she%20brings%20home%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20debris%20after%20those%20outings.%20I'm%20also%20a%20spiller%20and%20drop%20bits%20of%20what%20I'm%20cooking%20or%20working%20with%20onto%20the%20floor%2C%20so%20my%20home%20can%20quickly%20spiral%20out%20of%20control%20unless%20I%20vacuum%20daily.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20Stratos%20Cordless%20Vacuum%20meets%20my%20needs%20exceptionally%20well.%20I%20was%20most%20impressed%20with%20its%20ability%20to%20pick%20up%20debris%20both%20big%20and%20small.%20While%20this%20vacuum%20sometimes%20had%20trouble%20with%20extra-fine%20materials%20like%20the%20sand%20that%20my%20pup%20carried%20in%20following%20a%20swim%2C%20it%20had%20no%20issue%20gathering%20larger%20items%20such%20as%20stray%20filling%20from%20my%20dog's%20toys%2C%20slices%20of%20onion%20I%20dropped%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20and%20most%20impressively%2C%20large%20pieces%20of%20hard%20plastic%20from%20my%20dog's%20chewed%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Stratos%20performed%20well%20during%20our%20standardized%20testing%2C%20where%20we%20tried%20the%20vacuum%20on%20hard%20floors%20and%20carpets%20with%20materials%20like%20flour%2C%20sugar%2C%20kibble%2C%20and%20lentils.%20But%20its%20ability%20to%20suck%20up%20materials%20that%20naturally%20end%20up%20in%20my%20home%20was%20a%20huge%20selling%20point%20for%20me%20and%20is%20something%20my%20upright%20vacuum%20often%20fails%20to%20do.%20I%20loved%20that%20I%20could%20clean%20up%20almost%20anything%20on%20all%20three%20cleaning%20modes%20with%20little%20trouble.%20I%20also%20enjoyed%20how%20functional%20this%20model%20is.%20I%20could%20easily%20slide%20it%20beneath%20my%20bed%20and%20sofa%20for%20cleaning%20in%20hard-to-reach%20spots%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20bendable%20stick%20and%20swivel%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20powerful%20suction%20does%20come%20at%20a%20cost%3A%20the%20vacuum's%20battery%20life.%20The%20longest%20I%20could%20clean%20in%20the%20vacuum's%20standard%20mode%20was%20about%2030%20minutes%2C%20and%20that%20was%20only%20on%20easy%20cleaning%20jobs%20like%20picking%20up%20dirt%20from%20the%20hardwood%20floor.%20Shark%20advertises%2060%20minutes%20of%20battery%20life%20in%20Eco%20mode%20when%20using%20the%20vacuum%20as%20a%20handheld%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20even%20get%2015%20minutes%20of%20battery%20life%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20of%20the%20shark%20stratos%20cleaning%20flour%20on%20carpet%20and%20hard%20floor.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a2c0a58e7c0c29a28d965%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Shark%20Stratos%20Cordless%20Vacuum%20easily%20picked%20up%20flour%20on%20hardwood%20and%20carpet%20on%20all%20three%20power%20modes.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EEase%20of%20use%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20Stratos%20Cordless%20Vacuum%20is%20about%20as%20simple%20as%20it%20gets.%20The%20model's%20lack%20of%20a%20cord%20and%20easy%20maneuverability%20make%20it%20a%20fantastic%20choice%20for%20those%20who%20want%20to%20pass%20on%20a%20clunky%20vacuum.%20Both%20the%20full-size%20and%20handheld%20versions%20of%20this%20vacuum%20were%20also%20convenient%20to%20use%20at%20all%20times%20of%20day%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20LED%20headlights%20that%20illuminate%20the%20floor.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20bendable%20stick%20and%20swivel%20head%2C%20the%20vacuum%20has%20a%20press%20button%20to%20control%20its%20power%20and%20mode%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20this%20saves%20you%20from%20applying%20constant%20pressure%20to%20a%20power%20switch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Shark%20Stratos%20has%20three%20modes%20for%20cleaning%3A%20Clean%20Sense%20IQ%2C%20Eco%2C%20and%20Boost%20mode.%20Clean%20Sense%20IQ%20is%20what%20I%20primarily%20tested%2C%20as%20this%20is%20the%20power%20mode%20that's%20most%20suited%20for%20general%20cleaning.%20It%20uses%20an%20infrared%20sensor%20to%20increase%20or%20decrease%20power%20depending%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20debris%20it's%20picking%20up.%20Eco%20mode%20lowers%20power%20to%20save%20battery%2C%20although%20there%20wasn't%20much%20difference%20in%20power%20performance%20during%20our%20tests%20on%20this%20mode.%20Boost%20mode%2C%20the%20most%20powerful%20cleaning%20option%2C%20increases%20power%20during%20cleaning.%20This%20mode%20is%20best%20suited%20for%20heavy%20vacuuming%20jobs%20or%20picking%20up%20larger%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20vacuum%20on%20hardfloor%20vacuuming%20kibble.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a2c4958e7c0c29a28d99f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20vacuum%20excels%20at%20cleaning%20larger%20debris%20like%20kibble%20and%20bits%20of%20plastic%2C%20which%20is%20unusual%20for%20a%20cordless%20vacuum%20model.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3ECleaning%20performance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20hardwood%20and%20carpet%20vacuuming%2C%20this%20vacuum%20performed%20well.%20It%20excels%20at%20picking%20up%20oversize%20debris%20items%20and%20does%20so%20much%20better%20than%20my%20upright%20vacuum%20can.%20This%20model%20also%20picks%20up%20hair%20without%20getting%20it%20tangled%20in%20the%20brush%20roll%2C%20which%20I%20was%20thrilled%20by.%20The%20Shark%20Stratos%20struggled%20to%20clean%20especially%20fine%20materials%20like%20sand%20and%20sugar%20on%20the%20first%20pass%2C%20but%20one%20or%20two%20runs%20over%20this%20type%20of%20debris%20in%20the%20Boost%20mode%20(the%20most%20powerful%20mode%20on%20this%20model)%20cleaned%20it%20right%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20vacuum%20uses%20an%20infrared%20sensor%20when%20in%20Clean%20Sense%20IQ%20mode%20to%20increase%20or%20decrease%20cleaning%20power.%20I%20didn't%20notice%20this%20feature%20other%20than%20from%20a%20noise%20perspective.%20The%20vacuum%20would%20get%20louder%20if%20the%20sensor%20indicated%20a%20heavy%20debris%20pile%2C%20but%20otherwise%2C%20I%20did%20not%20notice%20any%20significant%20performance%20increase%20when%20the%20infrared%20sensor%20boosted%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close%20up%20of%20the%20brush%20and%20dustbin%20for%20the%20Shark%20Stratos%20Cordless%20Vacuum.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656a425386933e8fdb2eff47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dustbin%20can%20be%20challenging%20to%20clean%20due%20to%20its%20unusual%20shape%2C%20but%20cleaning%20the%20brush%20roll%20is%20a%20breeze.%20Its%20anti-tangle%20feature%20prevents%20hair%20from%20clogging%20it.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3EDustbin%20and%20Maintenance%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dustbin%20is%20easily%20emptied%20but%20tough%20to%20clean%20due%20to%20its%20odd%20shape.%20After%20testing%20this%20vacuum%20on%20spilled%20flour%2C%20I%20still%20have%20flour%20coating%20the%20inside%20of%20the%20dustbin%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20times%20I've%20opened%20the%20bin%20to%20clean%20it.%20I%20also%20need%20to%20empty%20the%20dustbin%20often%20as%20it's%20small%20and%20fills%20quickly.%20That%20can%20be%20frustrating%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20tiny%20element%20of%20upkeep%20on%20an%20otherwise%20low-maintenance%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EBattery%20Life%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20other%20cordless%20vacuums%2C%20the%20battery%20life%20of%20the%20Shark%20Stratos%20Cordless%20Vacuum%20is%20less%20than%20I%20would%20like.%20This%20model%20needs%20a%20full%20charge%20to%20run%20well.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20will%20lose%20significant%20power%20after%20just%2010%20minutes%20of%20use.%20I%20do%20like%20that%20there%20is%20a%20power%20indicator%20on%20the%20LED%20display%20screen%2C%20which%20tells%20you%20how%20much%20battery%20you%20have%20left.%20The%20vacuum%20also%20doesn't%20lose%20its%20suction%20power%20as%20the%20battery%20decreases%3A%20Once%20it's%20dead%2C%20the%20vacuum%20will%20just%20turn%20off.%20Some%20cordless%20vacuums%20I've%20tried%20will%20slowly%20lose%20power%20as%20the%20battery%20decreases%2C%20so%20I%20like%20that%20this%20vacuum%20is%20as%20strong%20at%2010%25%20battery%20as%20it%20is%20at%20100%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFiltration%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20vacuum%20uses%20a%20foam%20and%20felt%20HEPA%20filter%20that%20is%20washable%20for%20repeated%20use.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Findoor-air-quality-iaq%2Fwhat-hepa-filter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHEPA%20filters%3C%2Fa%3E%20trap%20pollen%2C%20dust%2C%20and%20other%20small%20debris%20more%20effectively%20than%20non-HEPA%20filters%2C%20and%20they%20are%20usually%20the%20standard%20filter%20option%20in%20most%20contemporary%20vacuums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20Consider%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20low%20battery%20life%20makes%20this%20vacuum%20struggle%20to%20keep%20up%20during%20longer%20cleaning%20sessions.%20I%20had%20to%20recharge%20it%20at%20least%20once%20to%20vacuum%20my%20entire%20860-square-foot%20apartment.%20I'll%20admit%20I'm%20a%20thorough%20vacuumer%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20vac%20that%20can%20run%20for%20hours%20during%20deep%20cleaning%2C%20I%20would%20suggest%20opting%20for%20an%20upright%20plug-in%20vacuum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20vacuum%20is%20also%20expensive.%20Although%20cordless%20models%20tend%20to%20run%20a%20higher%20price%20tag%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20this%20product%20might%20not%20be%20worth%20it