osts-results-side-effects%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGroundbreaking%20medications%20like%20semaglutide%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20not%20only%20game-changers%20for%20weight%20loss%20and%20diabetes%20treatment%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20part%20of%20a%20group%20of%20drugs%20that%20could%20stave%20off%20other%20health%20issues%20such%20as%20colon%20cancer%2C%20new%20research%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESemaglutide%2C%20sold%20under%20the%20brand%20names%20Wegovy%20and%20Ozempic%2C%20is%20a%20type%20of%20medication%20known%20as%20a%20GLP-1%20receptor%20agonist.%20Drugs%20in%20this%20category%20are%20often%20used%20to%20manage%20blood%20sugar%20and%20control%20appetite%2C%20and%20work%20by%20acting%20on%20a%20hormone%20in%20the%20body%20which%20helps%20regulate%20insulin.%20The%20newest%20class%20of%20these%20drugs%20are%20once-weekly%20injections%2C%20compared%20to%20daily%20injections%20for%20older%20variations%20like%20liraglutide%20(brand%20name%20Saxenda).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20the%20Case%20Western%20Reserve%20University%20wanted%20to%20see%20how%20this%20class%20of%20drugs%20might%20play%20a%20role%20in%20preventing%20colon%20cancer%20compared%20to%20other%20diabetes%20drugs%2C%20since%20the%20diseases%20can%20go%20hand%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20looked%20at%20data%20from%20more%20than%201%20million%20patients%20with%20type%202%20diabetes%20who%20were%20prescribed%20medication%20to%20treat%20it%20for%20the%20first%20time%20between%202005%20and%202019.%20The%20researchers%20then%20compared%20the%20rates%20of%20colon%20cancer%20diagnosis%20between%20patients%20on%20different%20drugs%20over%2015%20years%20of%20follow%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatients%20on%20GLP-1%20medications%20had%20a%2044%25%20lower%20risk%20of%20developing%20colon%20cancer%20compared%20to%20patients%20on%20insulin%2C%20according%20to%20the%20findings%2C%20published%20December%207%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamaoncology%2Ffullarticle%2F2