eachers%20to%20a%20constant%20cycle%20of%20contract%20renewals%20every%20four%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Apoorvanand%20highlighted%20the%20open%20secret%20of%20political%20affiliations%20playing%20a%20decisive%20role%20in%20appointments%2C%20especially%20if%20recommended%20by%20sources%20linked%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%20Instances%20of%20individuals%20expressing%20gratitude%20to%20RSS-affiliated%20figures%2C%20such%20as%20DUTA%20President%20A.K.%20Bhagi%2C%20further%20fuel%20suspicions%20of%20a%20political%20bias%20in%20hiring%20and%20firing%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20have%20also%20voiced%20concerns%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20political%20affiliations%20on%20the%20academic%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20practice%20of%20favouring%20political%20connections%20over%20merit%20persists%2C%20questions%20arise%20about%20the%20longstanding%20nature%20of%20this%20issue%20and%20its%20contribution%20to%20the%20erosion%20of%20educational%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FBq7oCoZRm8Y%3Fsi%3DMkcO-zXbZ8FCidVZ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701961208000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07192337%2FIMG_6223.00_15_59_09.Still002.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-removal-of-ramjas-colleges-ad-hoc-teachers-raises-concerns-about-dus-academic-standards%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20arbitrary%20removal%20of%20ad%20hoc%20teachers%20has%20become%20a%20concerning%20trend%2C%20with%2075%25%20already%20displaced%20by%20April%202023%2C%20raising%20alarms%20about%20the%20fairness%20of%20the%20ad%20hoc%20system%20and%20