ne%20education%20plan%2C%20Kuki%20students%20from%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20hill%20areas%20opted%20for%20admission%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fkuki-students-look-to-the-rest-of-india-for-their-higher-studies%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Kannur%20University.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDead%20bodies%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETribal%20leaders%20also%20denied%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20regarding%20the%20acceptance%20of%20dead%20bodies%2C%20questioning%20the%20committee%20for%20not%20meeting%20them%20and%20addressing%20their%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20COTU%2C%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20taken%20on%20a%20tour%20by%20the%20state%20authorities%20who%2C%20according%20to%20the%20tribals%2C%20have%20assisted%20the%20assailants%2C%20has%20its%20own%20problems%20regarding%20who%20the%20committee%20is%20introduced%20to%20by%20state%20officials%20for%20interaction.%20We%20would%20recommend%20that%20after%20completing%20the%20tour%20organised%20by%20the%20state%2C%20the%20above%20mentioned%20tribal%20organisations%20be%20consulted%20for%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20victim%E2%80%99s%20areas%20so%20that%20the%20committee%20may%20get%20accurate%20information%20from%20the%20tribal%20and%20victim%E2%80%99s%20point%20of%20view.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F25175627%2Fimage-1085.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22772%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F25175627%2Fimage-1085.png%20772w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F25175627%2Fimage-1085-300x223.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-660062%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20silent%20march%20in%20Manipur%20on%20June%2024%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENine%20burial%20sites%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBased%20on%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20issued%20directives%20for%20the%20burial%20or%20cremation%20of%20all%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20the%20state%2C%20including%20the%2088%20that%20have%20been%20identified%20but%20not%20claimed%20by%20their%20next%20of%20kin%2C%20by%20December%2011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdding%20to%20this%2C%20the%20court%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEither%20the%20relatives%20of%20the%20deceased%20can%20accept%20the%20bodies%20and%20perform%20their%20last%20rites%20at%20any%20of%20the%20nine%20burial%20sites%20identified%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20or%20the%20state%20can%20go%20ahead%20and%20do%20the%20same%20in%20accordance%20with%20municipal%20law%2C%20the%20court%20ordered.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Freport-in-sc-on-manipur-victims-bodies-in-morgues-highlights-deep-divides-state-of-law-and-order%5C%22%3EReport%20in%20SC%20on%20Manipur%20Victims%E2%80%99%20Bodies%20in%20Morgues%20Highlights%20Deep%20Divides%2C%20State%20of%20Law%20and%20Order%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20press%20note%2C%20ITLF%20and%20COTU%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20bodies%20of%20our%20community%20people%20since%20May%203%2C%20we%20have%20raised%20this%20issue%20multiple%20times%2C%20including%20to%20Amit%20Shah%20when%20he%20was%20here%20in%20Manipur.%E2%80%9D%20The%20tribal%20leader%20also%20added%20that%20the%20state%20has%20all%20the%20facilities%20and%20if%20they%20have%20the%20intention%20to%20return%20the%20bodies%2C%20then%20they%20should%20have%20returned%20them%20by%20helicopter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20leader%20of%20the%20Kuki%20Students%20Organisation%20(KSO)%2C%20in%20a%20telephonic%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Freport-in-sc-on-manipur-victims-bodies-in-morgues-highlights-deep-divides-state-of-law-and-order%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Econversation%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Cspan%3Ealso%20questioned%20the%20Manipur%20government%20on%20not%20letting%20tribal%20Leaders%20enter%20Imphal%20to%20verify%20and%20claim%20the%20bodies%20lying%20in%20the%20capital%E2%80%99s%20hospitals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECompensation%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20compensation%20plan%20announced%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20in%20June%2C%20the%20committee%20stated%20in%20court%20that%20there%20were%20a%20few%20families%20who%20had%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20compensation%20offered%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20be%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20dead%20to%20accept%20money%20at%20this%20stage%20from%20the%20very%20state%20that%20engineered%20the%20ethnic%20cleansing.%20Hence%20the%20overall%20feeling%20is%20that%20after%20the%20dead%20bodies%20are%20buried%20with%20dignity%20according%20to%20tribal%20customs%2C%20then%20a%20decision%20can%20and%20will%20be%20taken%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%20regarding%20compensation%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20tribal%20organisations%20said%20in%20response.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EReconstruction%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kuki%20community%20also%20questioned%20the%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20on%20not%20initiating%20the%20construction%20of%20tribal%20houses%20and%20churches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20said%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20comprehend%20how%20the%20committee%E2%