3%2F11%2FChitale_11zon-1700660560-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334699%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20bakarwadi%20at%20Chitale%20is%20famous%20and%20thousands%20of%20kgs%20are%20prepared%20everyday%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%20is%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20brand%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBakarwadi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%20Few%20know%20that%20this%20was%20the%20result%20of%20a%20Maharashtra%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20idea.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaskar%20Ganesh%20Chitale%20turned%20to%20farming%20to%20help%20his%20widowed%20mother.%20However%2C%20hours%20spent%20at%20the%20farm%20in%20the%20drought-prone%20village%20of%20Limbgove%2C%2020%20km%20from%20Satara%2C%20yielded%20few%20to%20no%20returns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201939%2C%20Chitale%20boarded%20a%20train%20to%20Bhilawadi%20in%20Sangli%20district%20where%20he%20observed%20an%20abundance%20of%20domesticated%20animals.%20Milk%20would%20often%20be%20in%20excess.%20The%20farmer%20decided%20to%20put%20this%20to%20use%20and%20began%20making%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252594%2Fchitale-bandhu-mithai-bakarwadi-babasaheb-bhaskar-ganesh-chitale-shrikhand-mango-burfi-peda-indian-icons-yos191%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilk%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20cottage%20cheese%2C%20shrikhand%2C%20milk%20powder%2C%20etc.%20Today%2C%20over%2040%2C000%20farmers%20work%20with%20the%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bakarwadi%20sold%20by%20the%20brand%20is%20so%20famous%20that%20over%201%2C000%20kgs%20are%20made%20in%20an%20hour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Vadilal%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99ve%20all%20enjoyed%20the%20popsicles%20on%20a%20sunny%20afternoon%20after%20the%20end-of-year%20exams.%20The%20name%20%E2%80%98Va