0and%20irrigation%20canals%20completely%20drying%20up%2C%20cultivation%20in%20the%20parched%20land%20of%20the%20Osmanabad%20district%20has%20become%20exhausting%20for%20farmers.%20Lying%20under%20the%20rain%20shadow%20region%20of%20Marathwada%2C%20the%20district%20faces%20acute%20water%20scarcity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20input%20costs%20and%20unfair%20market%20prices%20have%20severely%20affected%20the%20output%20and%20yield%20of%20the%20major%20crops%20of%20the%20region%20%E2%80%94%20like%20soybean%2C%20sugarcane%2C%20sorghum%2C%20and%20millet.%20The%20compounding%20debts%20put%20Maharashtra%20farmers%20under%20a%20huge%20economic%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20the%20recurring%20droughts%20force%20farmers%20to%20sometimes%20end%20their%20lives.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncrb.gov.in%2Fuploads%2Fnationalcrimerecordsbureau%2Fpost%2F169599016203ADSI-2021Chapter-2Suicides-ExcludingFarmerCauses.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENCRB%3C%2Fa%3E)%20data%3C%2Fem%3E%20revealed%20that%20a%20total%20of%2010%2C881%20persons%20involved%20in%20the%20farming%20sector%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%202021.%20With%2037.3%20percent%2C%20Maharashtra%20accounted%20for%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20farmer%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20a%20bunch%20of%20impoverished%20farmers%20have%20turned%20to%20cultivating%20oyster%20pearls%20in%20the%20water-starved%20Marathwada%20to%20overcome%20the%20challenges%20posed%20by%20recurring%20droughts%20and%20low%20crop%20yields.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20farmer%20is%20Sanjay%20Narsing%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20nine%20other%20small-scale%20farmers%2C%20Sanjay%20harvested%208%2C000%20pearls%20in%20an%20acre%20of%20pond%2C%20earning%20them%20Rs%2040%20lakh.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nore