%20Signs%E2%80%99%3A%20What%20It%20Means%20to%20Be%20Children%20Of%20Deaf%20Adults%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20excitement%20of%20a%20crowd%20can%20be%20either%20a%20very%20thrilling%20or%20a%20very%20daunting%20experience%20for%20us.%20If%20you%20are%20a%20child%2C%20then%20this%20can%20easily%20shape%20your%20outlook%20on%20life%20and%20personality.%20But%20for%20one%20such%20young%20person%2C%20back%20in%202015-16%2C%20participating%20in%20protests%20was%20a%20way%20of%20life.%20For%20Sarah%20Sharma%2C%20this%20was%20routine.%20Being%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328341%2Fyunikee-empowers-deaf-persons-accessing-hearing-solutions-govt-jobs-skills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChild%20Of%20Deaf%20Adults%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20a%20CODA%2C%20fighting%20for%20her%20parents%E2%80%99%20rights%20was%20personal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20when%20the%20Rights%20of%20Persons%20with%20Disabilities%20Act%20(RPwD%20Act%2C%202016)%20was%20being%20passed%2C%20I%20was%20there%20with%20my%20parents%2C%20protesting%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Delhi%20and%20interpreting%20for%20them%20with%20the%20police%20and%20other%20officials.%20I%20must%20have%20been%207%20or%208%20and%20the%20entire%20experience%20was%20quite%20scary%20because%20I%20was%20a%20child%20after%20all%20talking%20to%20adults%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Sarah%2C%20now%20training%20to%20professionally%20be%20an%20Indian%20Sign%20Language%20(ISL)%20interpreter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSign%20language%20was%20my%20first%20language.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F292576%2Fdeaf-mute-kashmiri-artist-carves-wooden-sculptures-earns-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoth%20my%20parents%20are%20Deaf%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20sign%20language%20is%20my%20mother%20tongue.%20That%20is%20how%20we%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%2C%E